"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/rooms#amenities\">Amenities</a></li><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"text-xs tracking-widest uppercase font-sans text-warm-gray hover:text-charcoal transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"hidden md:inline-block btn-primary text-xs py-2.5 px-6\" href=\"/booking\">Book Now</a><button class=\"md:hidden flex flex-col gap-1.5 p-2\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-px bg-charcoal transition-all \"></span></button></nav></header><main><section class=\"pt-40 pb-20 bg-charcoal\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12\"><p class=\"section-label text-gold\">Book a Viewing</p><h1 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,6rem)] font-light text-cream leading-none\">Begin your<br/><span class=\"italic\">journey home</span></h1></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-1 space-y-10\"><div><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-gold font-sans mb-4\">What to expect</p><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"font-display text-3xl text-stone font-light leading-none\">01</span><p class=\"text-warm-gray text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed pt-1\">Fill in your details and preferred viewing time.</p></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"font-display text-3xl text-stone font-light leading-none\">02</span><p class=\"text-warm-gray text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed pt-1\">Our team confirms within 24 hours.</p></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"font-display text-3xl text-stone font-light leading-none\">03</span><p class=\"text-warm-gray text-sm font-sans leading-relaxed pt-1\">Arrive and experience Belmont in person.</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"border-t border-stone pt-8\"><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-gold font-sans mb-4\">Contact us directly</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm font-sans text-warm-gray\"><p>+233 24 456 9540</p><p>stenadu@gmail.com</p><p class=\"pt-2 text-xs\">Mon–Sat, 24hr</p></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><div class=\"space-y-8\"><div><p class=\"text-xs tracking-superwide uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-6\">Your Details</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div><label class=\"block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-2\">First Name</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Kwame\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal placeholder:text-warm-gray/40 outline-none focus:border-charcoal transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-2\">Last Name</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Mensah\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal placeholder:text-warm-gray/40 outline-none focus:border-charcoal transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-2\">Email Address</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"kwame@email.com\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal placeholder:text-warm-gray/40 outline-none focus:border-charcoal transition-colors\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-2\">Phone Number</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"+233 20 000 0000\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal placeholder:text-warm-gray/4