umber of Guests</label><input type=\"number\" min=\"1\" max=\"6\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal outline-none focus:border-charcoal transition-colors\" value=\"1\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6 gap-2\"><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">9:00 AM</button><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">10:30 AM</button><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">12:00 PM</button><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">2:00 PM</button><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">3:30 PM</button><button class=\"py-2.5 text-xs font-sans border transition-all duration-200 border-stone text-warm-gray hover:border-charcoal\">5:00 PM</button></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-warm-gray font-sans mb-2\">Additional Notes</label><textarea rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"Any specific requirements or questions...\" class=\"w-full border-b border-stone bg-transparent py-3 text-sm font-sans text-charcoal placeholder:text-warm-gray/40 outline-none focus:border-charcoal transition-colors resize-none\"></textarea></div><button class=\"btn-primary text-xs w-full md:w-auto disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\">Request Viewing</button></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-charcoal text-cream\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-20\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"md:col-span-2\"><p class=\"font-display text-4xl font-light mb-6\">Belmont</p><p class=\"t